The paper is about intrusion detection systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses machine learning techniques such as anomaly detection and Bayesian networks, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with network-based systems (NIDS) and host-based systems (HIDS), which are related to the sub-categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
